                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d505">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Count Wydenbruck</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Seward.</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Oakland, Md.,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-06-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 21, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Many thanks. Just received this second telegram :</p>
                <p>Imperial family consents to eventual reintegration of Prince Maximilian. Try to
                    let him know this.</p>
                <p rend="right">BEUST.</p>
                <p>May I hope that, if possible, this wish of my court may be fulfilled through your
                    exceedingly kind medium.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WYDENBRUCK.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward</hi>, <hi rend="italic">&amp;c.,
                            &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
